{"product_id":"madara-come-closer-infinite-lash-mascara-6ml","title":"MÁDARA Come Closer Infinite Lash Mascara, 6ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover the outstanding combination of effortless volume and well-defined separation with the Come Closer Infinite Lash Mascara. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe natural certified formula stars vegan waxes to ensure smooth application and lasting performance, while plant-derived peptides and organic castor oil encourage fuller, stronger lashes over time.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFeaturing a unique conical shape, the classic fibre brush coats each lash in jet black, all-natural pigment to give enviable volume, length and definition.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply one coat to clean lashes for a natural look, or use in layers to intensify. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e AQUA; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***; STEARIC ACID; HELIANTHUS ANNUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED CERA; GLYCERIN**; COPERNICIA CERIFERA (CARNAUBA) WAX; OLEA EUROPAEA (OLIVE) OIL UNSAPONIFIABLES; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; CELLULOSE; PENTYLENE GLYCOL; PULLULAN; OCTYLDODECANOL; GLYCERYL STEARATE; PISUM SATIVUM PEPTIDE; POLYGLYCERYL-10 LAURATE; SORBITOL; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; SHOREA ROBUSTA RESIN; GLYCERYL CAPRYLATE\/ CAPRATE; PALMITIC ACID; POTASSIUM HYDROXIDE; ACACIA SENEGAL GUM; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; XANTHAN GUM; TREHALOSE; CITRIC ACID; LEUCONOSTOC\/RADISH ROOT FERMENT FILTRATE; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using Organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636200206663,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-come-closer-infinite-lash-mascara-6ml-7855214.jpg?v=1762389187","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-come-closer-infinite-lash-mascara-6ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}